revisions.rev:
'''Unpaid workers''' are those who [[employment|work]] without [[wage|pay]]. These may be either members of a [[family]] or [[cooperative]]; [[conscripts]] or [[forced labour]]; [[volunteer]] workers who work for [[charity (practice)|charity]] or [[amusement]]<ref>{{citation |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=q5QOAAAAQAAJ |title=Volunteers |author=Jone L. Pearce}}</ref>; [[student]]s who take [[intern]] positions as [[work experience]]; or conventional workers who are not paid because their enterprise is short of [[money]] or subject to [[embezzlement]].
